data.description: This condo offers Columbus taxes in a prime location just minutes from the freeway and shopping! Move in ready and maintenance free, This condo has a finished basement, that has a half bath, storage,  laundry area, and a large additional living space. The first floor is open to the kitchen that leads to the outdoor paver patio. The 2nd level offers two generous sized  bedrooms and a full bath. Updates include new HVAC March 2024, new dishwasher March 2024, new sliding glass door March 2024, and refurbished hardwood floors
